Background This Statement of Work defines the client's request to submit {API} API requests for users via CSV upload. Purpose This Statement of Work covers the allowable scope of the project. Any term not defined herein shall have the meaning set forth in the Attentive Master Subscription Agreement or the relevant Order Form.
Specification Client will upload files to: {fileNameAndDate} {filename} represents the path and filename. {[[dateFormat]]} represents the date the file will be processed. The file will be in {fileType} format The file will contain a header row that lists the field names. Each data row will include the field values. The file will be processed {frequency} at {triggerTime} ({timezone} time) API Payload The fields in the file will be mapped to the API as shown in the payload below, where API property names are listed on the left, and field names are displayed in curly braces on the right.
